# Android Multi-User Local-First

Android will be used by many field engineers.

Required:
- active session
- switch user
- logout without deleting pending sync
- project assignment cache
- permission snapshot
- sync outbox per user
- audit log per user/device/session

Every local operation must include:
- localUserId
- serverUserId
- userUuid
- deviceId
- sessionId

Never send User A outbox as User B.
